Package: quickselect
Title: Quickly select data frame columns
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Cameron",
           family = "Kay",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "cameronstuartkay@gmail.com")
Description: Quickly select data frame or tibble columns using regex. It is essentially a wrapper for `select(matches("my_var"))` from dyplr.  
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
